            "notes": "The main concept of this deck is to utilize the Aggro archetype with the commander Spider-Man 2099 to overwhelm the opponent with a mix of aggressive creatures and efficient spells. The deck includes a combination of powerful spells like Lightning Bolt, Counterspell, and Force Spike to control the board and disrupt the opponent's game plan. Additionally, it includes creatures like True-Name Nemesis and Brazen Borrower to apply pressure and close out the game quickly. The deck also features various utility lands and cantrips like Ponder and Brainstorm to ensure consistency and smooth gameplay. By combining aggressive creatures with powerful spells and efficient card draw, this deck aims to assert dominance early and maintain control throughout the game."
